      "answer": "",
      "image": "qn_cl_tomas.png"
    },
    {
      "npc": "{user_nick}",
      "question": "\n<FONT color=#662500>我可不是小孩子……</FONT>",
      "answer": ""
    },
    {
      "npc": "学者百合花",
      "question": "ndnpc_MR_Jasmin_sp_05.ogg}<br>嗯，那又怎么样？只要能派上用场就行。<br>不要忘了，你是我们最后的希望……",
      "answer": ""
